dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Zoning_2018.gdb. [Calumet County zoning delineation that corresponds to the Zoning Ordinance passed in 2009. Zoning Districts: Wetland (W), Exclusive Agricultural Wetland (EAW), Natural Area (NA), Exclusive Agricultural (EA), General Agricultural (GA), Heartland (HL), Small Estate Residential (SE), Single Family Residential-20,000 (SF20), Single Family Residential-10,000 (SF10), High Density Residential (HD), Mixed Use Commercial (MC), Recreational Commercial (RC), Commercial Center (CC), Light Industrial (LI), Industrial (I).]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
